["Gerrit Thomas Ferreira also known as GT Ferreira is a South African businessman and banker who is the Chairman of RMI Holdings. He is also one of the co-founders of Firstrand bank in South Africa.","Gerrit Ferreira got his MBA degree from University of Stellenbosch. In 1977, he co-founded FirstRand's predecessor, Rand Consolidated Investing along with Paul Harris and Lauritz Dippenaar. Previously, he served as MD of RMB Holdings between 1985\u201388.[2]"]